---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 152
  - Title: Cruden's Concordence
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Renunciation-Detachment=The Rupture With Habit
Reference:
  Title: Galations
  Location: V 17
---
The Spirit of God stirs up motions and desires in the saints contrary to
those of the flesh, or unrcnewed part in man. and inclines them to desire
and endeavour the utter destruction of it.
